article_title: Thousands in U.S. stuck in Medicaid coverage gap
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Sun and clouds mixed. A stray severe thunderstorm is possible. High 68F. Winds S at 15 to 25 mph..

Tonight

Some clouds this evening will give way to mainly clear skies overnight. A stray severe thunderstorm is possible. Low 42F. Winds WSW at 10 to 15 mph.

article_metadata.author: James Chilton  jchilton@wyomingnews.com

og.description: CHEYENNE — When the U.S. Supreme Court upheld the constitutionality of the Affordable Care Act in 2012, the ruling came with a caveat.
